name: Teriyaki Chicken Wraps
author: Anonymous
summary: Fast and yummy Chicken Wraps using Teriyaki Sauté Express ® Sauté Starter.
ingredients: 2 squares Land O'Lakes® Teriyaki Saute Express®
1 pound boneless, skinless chicken breasts, cut into strips
3  green onions, diagonally cut into 1-inch pieces
directions: Combine cabbage and carrots in bowl; set aside
Melt Saute Express® squares in 12-inch nonstick skillet over medium-low heat just until bubbles begin to form
Cook, stirring occasionally, 5 to 7 minutes or until chicken is no longer pink in center
Add cashews and green onions; stir
Continue cooking 1 to 2 minutes or until heated through
Place 1/4 chicken mixture onto each tortilla; top with 1/4 cabbage mixture
Fold 2 opposite sides of tortilla over filling
Starting at open end, roll up tightly to enclose filling
